### Step 1：初始化录屏实例
```
const chunks = new Set()
function createRecord () {
  const mediaStream = $canvas.captureStream(10) // 设置帧频率(FPS)
  mediaRecord = new MediaRecorder(mediaStream, {
      videoBitsPerSecond: 8500000
  })
  mediaRecord.ondataavailable = (e) => { // 接收数据
      chunks.add(e.data)
  }
}
```
### Step 2：控制录屏
